  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Sometime once, he [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] conducted one choir of-- based on the one oratory, oratory of Haydn, with amateur singers.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] Of course, very soon after that, he disappeared appear, together with number of other my cousins.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, first of all, what happened was that in-- little bit after the year of 1940, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the thing start to drastically change.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Actually, before-- little before that, all the time-- any time when I was descending to play in the garden with the other boys from the neighborhood there, I felt already different attitudes toward me.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By other little bit older boys, even-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I never will forget when I was-- I went there and was one summer day.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't recall when was '39 or till '40.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was playing there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one of the older boy was looking me and watching and starting to throw, first of all, sand toward me, until he started to throw sand over my eyes.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then I start to cry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he screamed, you dirty Jew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why don't you go to your own country, or your own place?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I was perhaps three and a half or four years old.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "These were, were kind of first very [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] if it's possible to say slight symptoms there of new, new climates that were arriving the time in Bulgaria until one day we had to, to pack our-- some of our clothing and leave our home.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "First of all, we had to move out of our home, going in different part of the city, not very far from the synagogue.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But this was for very short period of time.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
